Package: polisapi
Title: Download and Manage Data from the WHO POLIS Database
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R:
  person(given = "Mohamed A.",
         family = "Yusuf",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "moyusuf@who.int",
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9339-4613"))
Description: Provides tools for downloading, updating, and managing polio
    surveillance data from the World Health Organization's Polio Information
    System (POLIS) database. Supports sequential and parallel data retrieval,
    incremental updates, regional filtering, and multiple output formats.
    Includes access to case data, laboratory specimens, environmental
    surveillance, vaccination campaigns, and geographic references.
